message: It is with the greatest of pleasure that the team can officially announce the return of Project Euler. The current website will go offline for a short period on Saturday 16 August 2014 at approximately 9am [BST] to restore full functionality.
story: Meligy shared a link to the group: Egyptian Geeks.
name: Project Euler Returns (Thu, 14 Aug 2014)
caption: projecteuler.net
description: As many of you will be aware it was discovered on Sunday 15 June 2014 that Project Euler had been hacked.
